dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.tip.nrb.CommonResourceInfo
dataStructure.description:
This object class defines the attributes that are common to all resource objects used in the MTOSI/MTNM interface. This class should merge up into its parent class. There is currently no merge-up stereotype to direct the implementation so the class has not been decorated.

This entity is optional
